<br>
The Grimling Runner is roughly a 90 min spawn. He ping-pongs the Grimling mines in Tenebrous Mountains and the Zone to Grim forest. He's about level 35 or so, and seems to be totally resistant to snares and roots. Other than that, he's a gimp.<br>
<br>
You take the Grimling Runner pack to So-And-So Rallic in Katta Castellum, and he gives you some exp and the Rallic pack Pattern.<br>
<br>
Head to Hollowshade Moor, and kill a bunch of Razorbeak Owlbears, and keep on the look-out for Perfect Owlbear Pelts. Don't even think about quading, cause they cast, and they can also summon, which stinks. One Ice Comet kills them, so they don't have much for HP, but they hit pretty damn hard for their level.<br>
<br>
After you've gotten your perfect owlbear pelt, head to Shadeweaver's Thicket. You need Shadeling Silk, which drops off the some of the skeletons, and also drops off the xaktra thingies. You need a Shadeling silk thread, and a Shadeling Silk Cord. You make the thread by combining two silks in a sewing kit, and you make the cord by combining three threads in a kit.<br>
<br>
Put the following in your sewing kit/loom:<br>
<br>
Perfect Owlbear Pelt<br>
Rallic Pack Pattern<br>
Shadeling silk Thread<br>
Shadeling silk Cord<br>
<br>
Hit combine. The Pack is trivial at 1 skill, so make sure you've at least put on point in tailoring.<br>
<br>
It's an 85% 10 slot bag and holds GIANT items. Probably one of the best bags in the game now. You can probably do this quest in 4-6 hours, less if you're lucky with the drops. <p><center><IMG SRC=http://www.interofficenetworks.com/demo/doh/sigpic3.jpg><br><center><Br>Grand Master Fisherman<Br>Master Brewer<Br>Master Chef<Br>Master of Begging<Br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=40980">Check out my Gear</a></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showMessage?topicID=11160.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showMessage?topicID=11161.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.emailToFriend?topicID=11131.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.threadControl?topicID=11131.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=11131.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=11131.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub23.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="graffeswi